Alembic is a lightweight database migration tool for SQLAlchemy.
Flask-Migrate is an extension that configures Alembic in the proper
way to work with your Flask and Flask-SQLAlchemy application.

Bind "Migrate" to app and db
Migrate(app, db)

Create migrations folder and configuration
flask db init

generate an initial migration
flask db migrate

apply the migration to the database
flask db upgrade


flask db --help